Thirukkural,is,a,simple,quotes,service,The,original,Thirukkural,is,a,collection,of,Tamil,couplets,that,discuss,various,aspects,of,life,The,service,provides,Thirukkural,in,native,Tamil,language,with,English,translations,The,API,allows,users,to,send,queries,to,fetch,kurals,based,on,a,number,of,specified,parameters,including,the,number,of,the,kural,to,return,It,uses,RESTful,calls,and,responses,are,formatted,in,XML,and,JSON